of the wounded were passersby he said none of the restaurants 
staff or customers was hurt 
the corniche where the bomb exploded is popular with sunday 
morning strollers 
twisted metal and glass shards from a nearby sixstory apartment 
building the mayfair casino and another restaurant were strewn 
